import React from 'react'

import { AppBar, Icon, IconButton, Toolbar, Typography, Stack, Button } from "@mui/material"
import BiotechIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Biotech'

export const Navbar = () => {
    return (
        <AppBar>
            <Toolbar>
                <IconButton size='large' edge='start' color='inherit' aria-label='logo'>
                    <BiotechIcon/>
                </IconButton>
                <Typography variant='h6' component='div' sx={{flexGrow: 1}}>
                    GENE-Works
                </Typography>
                <Stack direction='row' spacing={2}>
                    <Button color='inherit'>Graph 1</Button>
                    <Button color='inherit'>Graph 2</Button>
                    <Button color='inherit'>Graph 3</Button>

                </Stack>
            </Toolbar>
        </AppBar>
    )
}
